title: Equipment Identity IMEI number These
extract: International Mobile Equipment Identity (IMEI) number. Every mobile phone has a 15-digit IMEI number, which can be identified by the mobile phone service provider's network. It is on the back of the handset under the battery and can be found on most handsets by pressing *#06# on the phone keypad.May 18, 2016
